name: TICKETS: Electric Western New Year's Dance Party featuring Steelism, Old Time Photo Booth!
description:
Ladies and Gentlemen,

It's time to ring in 2014 in style! 1960s style!

Electric Western is proud to announce a New Year's Eve Celebration unlike any other:

Join us on December 31st for an elegant evening of dancing, DJs, live music, champagne, and complimentary photos from The Old Time Photobooth Co. to say hello to 2014 the right way. Experience The 5 Spot in true 1960s fashion! Put your best 1960s threads on and look sharp, this is New Year's Eve we're talking about! Dress up. Get down. Let's twist into 2014!

- ELECTRIC WESTERN DJ Sets to keep your toes tappin' and the drinks flowing. 50's and 60's rock and roll, soul, doo woo, swing, jump blues, girl groups and more!  

- A very special set by Nashville favorite's STEELISM

- Free Photo Booth provided by OLD TIME PHOTOBOOTH CO. to capture all your NYE glory

DO NOT WAIT to get your tickets! 

PRE SALE TICKETS: $15
DAY OF EVENT: $20

See you Tuesday December 31st for a very special New Year's Eve at The 5 Spot in East Nashville, Tennessee!

- your friends at Electric Western

**Group discounts for parties of 10 or more. Email info@electricwesternrecords.com for more info**

**NO PHYSICAL TICKETS WILL BE MAILED TO YOU. PLEASE PRINT OUT YOUR TICKET RECEIPT AND BRING IT WITH YOU ON NEW YEAR'S EVE TO SHOW TO THE DOOR CONCIERGE. 

**ONLINE TICKET SALES END AT 3 P.M. DAY OF EVENT.
